quran[93]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Taa Siin, ﾉ容en ko aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden e deftere ﾉ殿nngunde."
  27,2,"Ko nde Peewal e welo-welo wonan'de gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,3,"ﾆ‘en ﾉ兎 no ﾃｱiiﾉ殿 e Juulde nden ﾉ兎 totta askal on, kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 njananaa fii Laakara on."
  27,4,"Pellet, ﾉ兎en ﾉ兎 ngooﾅ極擁naani Laakara on, Min cuﾉ預nii ﾉ兎 golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 mbumo."
  27,5,"Ko ﾉ兎en ngoni ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 woodani ﾉ蓉m Lepte bonﾉ容 ﾉ容n, kamﾉ兎 ka Laakara ko kamﾉ兎 ngoni hayruﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  27,6,"E pellet, an haﾉ預 lonnginee Alqur'aanaare nden immorde ka ﾃ粗eﾃｱo gannduﾉ熔."
  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo ﾉ兎ynguure makko nden: ""Min dey, mi haynike yiite, mi addana on ka nge woni ﾉ熔n kumpital ma mi addana on docotal kuﾉ橡砥ngal, bela jo'o onon on itwoto."
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arnoo e magge, o noddaa: ﾆ隔um woni barkinaama on wonﾉ熔 ka yiite e ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 banﾅ菊 magge, e Senaare wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden."
  27,9,"Eey ma Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla Tedduﾉ熔 ﾃ粗eﾃｱﾉ熔 On."
  27,10,"Liﾉ砥 tuggordu maaﾉ預 ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hundu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mbooﾉ妖i, o hucciti ko o doguﾉ熔 o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: ""Wata a hul, Min dey Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kulataa to Am""."
  27,11,"Si wonaa oon tooﾃｱﾉ熔, refti o lomtini ko moﾆｴﾆｴi ﾉ殿awo bone ﾉ容n. Pellet, Min ko Mi cuhroowo Jurmeteeﾉ熔."
  27,12,"Naatnu junngo ma ngon ka jiiba maaﾉ預, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, [ﾉ蓉m no jeyaa] e ndeer aayeeje jeenay nulaaﾉ容 e Fir'awna e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, pellet, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 laatike yimﾉ兎 faasiqiiﾉ兎."
  27,13,"Tuma nde arnoo e maﾉ橡兎 Aayeeje amen ﾉ容n ko yi'eteeﾉ容, ﾉ兎 mbi'i: ""ﾆ隔'um, ko mbilewu ﾉ殿nngungu""."
  27,14,"ﾆ‘ njeddi [aayeeje ﾉ容n], tawi wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n no yananaa fii majje, tooﾃｱe e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,15,"Gooﾅ極擁i Min ngokkii Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Ganndal ﾉ兎 maaki: ""Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On ﾉ砥rnuﾉ熔 min e dow ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 immorde e jeyaaﾉ兎 makko gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  27,16,"Sulaymaana roni Daawuuda, O maaki: ""eey mon yimﾉ兎, min nganndinaama haala colli ﾉ擁n, men okkaama immorde e kala hu'unde, Pellet, ﾉ蓉mﾉ熔o ko ﾉ蓉m woni ﾉ砥ral ﾉ殿nngungal""."
  27,17,"Sulaymaana mooﾉ殿naa koneeli makko ﾉ擁 immorde ka jinnaaji e ka yimﾉ兎 e ka colli, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 yuﾉ橡妬naaﾉ兎."
  27,18,"Haa nde ﾉ兎 ngrnoo e aynde korndolli ﾉ擁n, korndolil mbi'i i'i: ""eey mon korndolli, naatee ka koﾉ預nﾉ擁 mooﾉ熔n, fii wata Sulaymaana e koneeli mu'um ﾉ擁n muncu on, tawa kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 tinaa""."
  27,19,"[Sulaymaana] moosi ko o jaluﾉ熔 immorde e konngol maggi ngol, o maaki: ""Jooma, lonnginam no mi yettira neema maaﾉ預 mo neeminﾉ預a e dow am on, e jibibinﾉ兎 lam ﾉ兎n, e nde mi gollata ko moﾆｴﾆｴi mbeltoraa ﾉ蓉m, naatnaami ka Yurmeende Maaﾉ預 wond'ude e jiyaaﾉ兎 Ma moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎""."
  27,20,"O ﾆｴewtii colli ﾉ擁n, o maaki: ""Ko heﾉ妬 kam, mi yiaani Hud-huda. Kaa ndu laati jiyaandu e wirniiﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n?"""
  27,21,"Maa mi lepta ndu sanne lepte caﾉ葉uﾉ容 ma maa mi hirsandu sanne, ma ndu addana kam hujja ﾉ殿nnguﾉ熔."
  27,22,"Ndu ﾃｱiiﾉ兎 ko woﾉ遼預ani, ndu wi'i: ""mi huﾉ妬ndike ko a huﾉ妬ndaaki ﾉ蓉m, mi addanii ma immorde to Saba'i kumpital yananaangal""."
  27,23,"Min dey, mi tawii sonnaajo no laamii ﾉ兎 homo okkaa immorde e kala hu'unde, no woodami mo kadi jullere [laamu] mawnde."
  27,24,"Mi tawii mo kaﾅ橘o e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n heﾉ兎 cujjana na'ange nge ga Alla; Seytaane no cuﾉ預niﾉ兎 golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n o faddii ﾉ兎 ga Laawol ngol, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 peewataa."
  27,25,"Ko haﾉ預ta ﾉ兎 cujjana Alla oon jaltinoowo ko suuﾉ擁i kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi homo Anndi ko cuuﾉ熔ton e ko peﾃｱinton."
  27,26,"Alla, Deweteeﾉ熔 alaa si wonaa Kaﾅ橘o Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin."
  27,27,"O maaki: ""Aray min ndaara si a gooﾅ極蓉, maaﾉ蓉m si laati jiyaaﾉ熔 e fenﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n""."
  27,28,"Yahdu e nduu talkuru am mbernoﾉ預a ndu ka maﾉ橡兎, refti kuccaa ﾉ兎 ndaaraa ko holﾉ蓉m ﾉ兎 nduttata."
  27,29,"[Sonnaajo on] wi'i: ""eey mon mbatu, min dey wernaama ka am talkuru teddundu""."
  27,30,"Pellet, nduu ko immorde e Sulaymaana, pellet, ko woni e mayru ko: ""Innde Alla kuuﾉ砥ﾉ熔 Yurmeende keeriiﾉ熔 Yurmeende Oon""."
  27,31,"Wota on townitano kam, ngaree e am ko jebbiliiﾉ兎."
  27,32,"O wi'i: ""eey mon mbatu, mbaﾉ葉ee kam e feere e ﾉ容e fiyaake am, mi laataaki taﾆｴoowo fiyaake haa tawteﾉ熔n e am""."
  27,33,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Enen ko en jooma doole e jooma hare caﾉ葉uﾉ容, fiyaake ﾉ容n ko ka maaﾉ預 woni, ndaaru ko holﾉ蓉m njamirtaa""."
  27,34,"[Debbo on] wi'i: ""Pellet, laamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n si ﾉ兎 naatii e saare ﾉ兎 mbonnat nde, ﾉ兎 mbaﾉ預 tedduﾉ兎 mayre ﾉ兎n hoyﾉ兎, ko wanonii ﾉ兎 ngollirta."
  27,35,"Awa miin, mi nulay e maﾉ橡兎 neldaari, mi ndaara ko holﾉ蓉m nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n nduttodata."
  27,36,"Tuma nde ﾉ兎 arnoo ka Sulaymaana, o maaki: ""Enee, on ﾉ兎ydiray kam jawdi, kon ko Alla okkimmi, no ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude diini kon ko O okki on, ko woni, onon hoﾉ熔n farnora neldaari mooﾉ熔n ndin""."
  27,37,"Rutto ka maﾉ橡兎, mamen ngaddana ﾉ兎 koneeli ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 maraa feere muuﾉ蓉m, mamen njaltin ﾉ兎 ton ko ﾉ兎 ja'asﾉ兎 hara kamﾉ兎 ko hoyﾉ兎."
  27,38,"O maaki: ""eey mon mbatu, ko hommbo e mooﾉ熔n addanta kam jullere laamu makko nden, ko adii ﾉ兎 arude ka am ko ﾉ兎 jebbiliiﾉ兎?"""
  27,39,"Ngaari jinna ndin wi'i: ""Min, mi addante nde ko adii a immaade e darnde maaﾉ預 nden, e pellet, min e dow ﾉ蓉m ko mi cemmbuﾉ熔 koolaaﾉ熔""."
  27,40,"Oon mo woni ka mu ganndal immorde ka deftere wi'i: ""Min mi anndante nde ko adii a nde ndarﾉ容 maaﾉ預 ﾉ容n ruttotoo e maaﾉ預"". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde ko nde ﾃｱiiﾉ砥nde ka makko, o maaki: ""ﾆ隔m ﾉ熔o, ko immorde e ﾆ「ral Joomi am, fii yo o ndarndo lam si mi jarnay [mo] maaﾉ蓉m si mi yeddat [mo], kala jarnuﾉ熔 anndu ko o jarni kon wonanay wonkii makko kin, kala yedduﾉ熔 kadi pellet, Joomi am ko o Galo Tedduﾉ熔""."
  27,41,"O maaki: ""Faytinanee mo jullere laamu makko nden, ndaaren si on annditat, kaa o laatoto jiyaaﾉ熔 e ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 anndittaa""."
  27,42,"Tuma nde o arnoo, [o] wi'aa: ""Enee, ko nii jullere maaﾉ預 nden wa'i?"" O wi'i: ""Awi'ayma ko kayre tigi nii"". Min ndokkaama ganndal ko adii mo, min laatii jebbiliiﾉ兎."
  27,43,"Faddii mo, ﾉ蓉m ko o laatinoo homo rewa ga Alla, pellet, kaﾅ橘o o laatinoke jiyaaﾉ熔 e yimﾉ兎 yedduﾉ兎."
  27,44,"Wi'anaa mo: ""Naatu ka huﾉ兎ere"". Tuma nde o yi'unoo nde o sikki ko nde duneere(tewru), o ﾃｱori dense (korle)makko ﾉ容n. [Sulaymaana] maaki: ""Pellet, ndee ko huﾉ兎ere newﾉ擁niraande ndaarorﾉ容"". [Debbo on] wi'i: ""Jooma, min dey mi tooﾃｱii woﾅ橘ii am, mi jebbilanike Alla Jooma winndire nden, wond'ude e Sulaymaana""."
  27,45,"Gooﾅ極擁i Min Nulii fa'ade e Samuudinkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n musiﾉ遼熔 maﾉ橡兎 on Saalihu, ﾉ蓉m woni rewee Alla. Tawi kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 feddeeji ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 hiﾉ兎 beeﾃｱondira."
  27,46,"O maaki: ""Ko onon yo yimﾉ兎 am, ko fii holﾉ蓉m heﾃｱornton bone ﾉ容n ko adii moﾆｴﾆｴere nden?"" ""Ko haﾉ擁 imsinanao Alla mbelejo'o onon on njurminoyte""."
  27,47,"ﾆ‘ mbi'i: ""Min kiitinorii ma e ﾉ兎n won'ﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 e maaﾉ預"". O maaki: ""kiite mooﾉ熔n on ko ka Alla woni, ko woni, onon ko on yimﾉ兎 fitneteeﾉ兎"""
  27,48,"Laatinoke ka saare ton worﾉ兎 njeenayo heﾉ兎 mbonna ka leydi ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴintaa."
  27,49,"ﾆ‘ mb'i: ﾆ‘ ngooﾉ溶dirii Alla, ma min waalanan mo ka suudu kaﾅ橘o e ﾉ兎ynguure makko nden refti ma min wi'an jeyﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n; men tawaaka bargol yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, e pellet, menen ko men gooﾅ極蓉ﾉ兎""."
  27,50,"ﾆ‘ kodi hodoore Minen kadi Min pewji fewjoore, tawi kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 so'ataa."
  27,51,"Ndaaru, ko honno laatorno battane hodo maﾉ橡兎 ngon, Minen Min njirbinno ﾉ兎 kamﾉ兎 e yimﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 fof maﾉ橡兎."
  27,52,"ﾆ格n cuuﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎 ko jeewuﾉ擁 sabu ko ﾉ兎 tooﾃｱunoo kon. Pellet, wonii e ﾉ蓉m Ma'ande wonan'de yimﾉ兎 haqqilooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,53,"Min danndi ﾉ兎n gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 ngoni hulooﾉ兎 [Alla]."
  27,54,"E Luutu, tuma nde o wi'anno yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n: 'Enee, on aray paﾅ橘are ﾉ容n hara hoﾉ熔n cutii?"""
  27,55,"Eyoo, onon on ngarat e worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka tuuyo ngccon rewﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n?! Si ko woni, onon ko on yimﾉ兎 majjaaﾉ兎."
  27,56,"Jaabawol yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ngonaano si wonaa ko ﾉ兎 mbi'i : ""Yaltinee yimﾉ兎 Luutu ﾉ兎n ka hoﾉ熔 (wura) mooﾉ熔n ; kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 laﾉ橡妬ntintooﾉ兎""."
  27,57,"Min daﾉ溶di mo kaﾅ橘o e yimﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, si wonaa debbo makko on; [on ﾉ熔n] Min hoddiranii mo ko o jiyaaﾉ熔 e halketaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,58,"Min toﾉ妬ni e dow maﾉ橡兎 toﾉ登, bonii toﾉ登 jeertinaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,59,"Maaku: Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, kisiyee wonii e jiyaaﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 O suﾉ妬i. Enee, ko Alla ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude, kaa ko ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁ﾉ兎 sirkanta?"
  27,60,"Kaa ko hommbo tagi kammuuji ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin O jippinani on immorde ka kammu ndiyam? Min puﾉ擁niri ﾉ預m gese joomiraaje ﾅ蟻ri. Wonantaa on nde puﾉ擁non leﾉ遼容 majje. Enee, hara deweteeﾉ熔 no woodi wond'ude e Alla? Ko woni, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 yimﾉ兎 ooﾃｱotooﾉ兎."
  27,61,"Kaa ko hommbo waﾉ擁 leydi ndin ﾃｱiiﾉ渡di, O waﾉ擁 hakkunde mayri calluﾉ擁 O waﾉ預ni ndi pelle o waﾉ擁 hakkunde maaje ﾉ容n ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 heedo?, hara na woodi deweteeﾉ熔 [goo] wond'ude e Alla? ko woni, ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de ﾉ兎n e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 nganndaa."
  27,62,"Kaa ko hommbo jaabato ﾉ妬ttiiﾉ熔 on si o noddi mo o hunca bone ﾉ容n o waﾉ預 on lontiiﾉ兎 ka leydi? Na woodi Koreweteeﾉ熔 goo wond'ude e Alla? Famﾉ擁i ko mbaajitoﾉ熔n."
  27,63,"Kaa ko hommbo feewnata on ka niﾉ兎 njoorndi e ka maayo, e ko hommbo accitata keni ﾉ擁n wewlinirayﾉ擁 fii Yurmeende Makko nden? Enee, ko deweteeﾉ熔 goo wond'ude e Alla? Alla Toowii ga ko ﾉ兎 cirkata kon."
  27,64,"Kaa ko hommbo woni puﾉ遼蓉ﾉ熔 tagoore nde refti O rutta ngu, e ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Enee, ko deweteeﾉ熔 goo wond'ude e Alla? Maaku: ""Addee daliili mooﾉ熔n on si tawii ko on gooﾅ極蓉ﾉ兎""."
  27,65,"Maaku: ""Anndaa ko wirnii kon ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wonaa Alla. ﾆ‘ so'ataa kadi ko honnde tuma ﾉ兎 immintinoytee""."
  27,66,"Ko woni, ganndal maﾉ橡兎 ngal hattii fii Laakara on, ko woni, kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 e sikke fii [Laakara], ko woni, kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 wumuﾉ兎 fii ﾉ蓉m."
  27,67,"ﾆ‘en yedduﾉ兎 mbi'i: "" Enee, hay si min laatike mbullaari e baabiraaﾉ兎 amen ﾉ兎n kadi, e hara minen ko min yaltinoyteeﾉ兎?"""
  27,68,"Gooﾅ極擁i min podanooma ﾉ蓉m minen e baabiraaﾉ兎 amen ko adii, ﾉ蓉m wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinooﾉ兎."
  27,69,"Maaku : ""njehee ka leydi ndaaron ko honno battane bonﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n laatornoo""."
  27,70,"Wota a suno fii maﾉ橡兎, wota a laato e ﾉ妬tteende immorde e ko ﾉ兎 peewjata kon."
  27,71,"Heﾉ兎 mb'a: ""Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike gooﾅ丘ﾉ遼兎?"""
  27,72,"Maaku: ""No tijjaa de tawata ﾉ殿danike on yoga e kon ko ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥ﾉ熔n yaccinaneede""."
  27,73,"Pellet, Joomi maaﾉ預 ko O Jom ﾆ「ral e dow yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en, kono ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de ﾉ兎n e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 njaarnataa [Alla]."
  27,74,"Pellet, Joomi maaﾉ預 hiMo Anndi ko ﾉ兎rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n coomi e ko ﾉ容 'eﾃｱﾃｱinta ko."
  27,75,"Alaa e birniikum ka kammu e ka leydi si wonaa [fii makkun] no e ndeer deftere ﾉ殿nngunde."
  27,76,"Pellet ndee Alqur'aanaare, hende filloo e dow ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 Israa'iila ﾉ兎n fii hu'unde nde ﾉ兎 ﾉ砥ri luutondirde nden e fii muuﾉ蓉m."
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonan'de gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maaﾉ預 O ﾃｱaawirat hakkunde maﾉ橡兎 ﾃ疎awoore makko ngal, ko Kaﾅ橘o woni Tedduﾉ熔 gannduﾉ熔."
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an haﾉ預 e hoore Goonga ﾉ殿nnguka ka."
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, a nanintaa fa'aﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n noddaandu ndun si ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉urnike ﾉ兎 nduﾅ喫tii."
  27,81,"An a wonaani peewnoowo wumﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e ga majjere maﾉ橡兎 nde. A nanintaa si wonaa ﾉ兎n gooﾅ極擁nﾉ兎 Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n hara kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 jebbiliiﾉ兎."
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow maﾉ橡兎, Min yaltinana ﾉ兎 daabewa immorde ka leydi himba kaalana ﾉ兎 won'nde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n laatike ﾉ兎 yananaaka aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n."
  27,83,"E ﾃｱande Min mooﾉ登yta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaaﾉ兎 e ﾉ兎n yennooﾉ兎 Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n hara kamﾉ兎 heﾉ兎 coggee."
  27,84,"Haa si ﾉ兎 ngarii, O Daala: ""Eyoo, on yenniino Aayeeje Am ﾉ容n, hara on huﾉ妬ndoraali ﾉ擁 ganndal. Kaa ko holﾉ蓉m wonﾉ熔n e gollude?"""
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e maﾉ橡兎 sabu ko ﾉ兎 tooﾃｱi ko, kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 kaalataa."
  27,86,"Enee, hara ﾉ兎 yiaani, Minen Min mbaﾉ擁i jemma on fii yo ﾉ兎 deeﾆｴu e maako, e ﾃｱalawma on nji'irﾉ熔? Pellet, wonii e ﾉ蓉m Aayeeje wonan'de yimﾉ兎 gooﾅ極擁nooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  27,87,"E ﾃ疎nde wuttoytee ka alaadu, ﾉ容nﾆｴoo ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 ka kammuuli e ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 ka leydi, si wonaa ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 Alla muuyi, gooto kala e maﾉ橡兎 aray e makko hara ko ﾉ兎 hoykiniiﾉ兎."
  27,88,"Haﾉ預 tina pelle ﾉ容n, cikka ko ﾉ容 fenndiiﾉ容, hara le kannje heﾉ容 wuloo wulagol duule ﾉ容n, ﾉ蓉um ko kuugal Alla, On ﾅ蟻rﾉ擁nﾉ熔 kala hu'unde, pellet, Kaﾅ橘o ko O kumpitiiﾉ熔 ko ngolloton kon."
  27,89,"Mo ardii e moﾆｴﾆｴere nden haray no woodani mo ko ﾉ砥ri nde moﾆｴﾆｴude, hara kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 hooliiﾉ兎 immorde e ﾉ容nﾆｴere nden ﾃ疎nde."
  27,90,"Mo ardii kadi e bone ﾉ容n, j'eece maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n kippete ka Yiite. Yalli on yoﾉ兎te si wonaa kon ko laatinoﾉ熔n hoﾉ熔n ngolla?"
  27,91,"Anndu ko mi yamiraa ko yo mi rewJooma ndii leydi ndi Alla harmini ﾉ蓉m, no woodani mo kala hu'unde. Mi yamiraama kadi yo mi laato jiyaaﾉ熔 e jebbiliiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  27,92,"E yo mi janngu Alqur'aanaare ndeen, mo feewii ko hoore-makko o feewani, mo majjii kadi maaku: ""Min dey, ko mi jiyaaﾉ熔 e jeertinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎en."
  27,93,"Maaku kadi: ""jettooje nden ngoodanii Alla, aray O holla on Aayeeje makko ﾉ容en ngaanndon ﾉ容"". Joomi maaﾉ預 wonaani belsindiiﾉ熔 ga e kon ko ngolloton."
